==== gc/br-on-non-null.wast ====
Wax type-checking should have failed (expected anyref, found funcref):
  fn f() {
      match (null as &?func) {
          null => {
              unreachable;
          }
          _ => {}
      }
  }
from wasm:
  (func
    block $l (result anyref)
      ref.null func
      br_on_non_null $l
      unreachable
    end
    drop
  )
